    </div>
    <div class="bg-about-bg4 text-base px-2.5 py-3 mb-2 rounded-lg text-center lg:text-left">
      Share privacy-protected interest profiles to increase relevance of content and offers
    </div>
    <div class="bg-about-bg4 text-base px-2.5 py-3 mb-2 rounded-lg text-center lg:text-left">
